    "name": "Stories of Home",
    "prerequisite": "*Campfire Chronicler Dedication*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You share the joy of every story of long-awaited homecoming you\u2019ve offered to Isthralei. You can spend 10 minutes sharing this joy with your allies within 30 feet. You and those allies regain Hit Points equal to their Constitution modifier (minimum 1) times their level and recover from the doomed, drained, and fatigued conditions as though they had a full night\u2019s rest (though they gain no other benefits associated with having a full night\u2019s rest).",
    "traits": [
